---
title: Balsamic-Glazed Pork Meatloaves with Thyme-Roasted Brussels Sprouts & Sweet Potato Jumble
description: We adore the comfort of meatloaf, which can easily be dressed up with whatever flavors we’re craving. In this fun riff on the classic, individual pork meatloaves are coated with a sweet-tangy-savory balsamic-plum glaze, and served with a pile of crisp, roasted sweet potatoes, red onion, and Brussels sprouts—indulgent and satisfying. It’s all about live, laugh, loaf!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/balsamic-glazed-pork-meatloaves-aabef78e.jpg
